def exchange(a, i, j):
   temp = a[i]
   a[i] = a[j]
   a[j] = temp

```

```
def shuffle(a):
    n = len(a)
    for i in range(n):
        r = random.randrange(i, n)
        exchange(a, i, r)

```

def randomarray(n):
    a = stdarray.create1D(n, 0.0)
    for i in range(n):
        a[i] = random.random()
    return a
